ent-RMCWeaponFlamerColony = LC9 incinerator unit
    .desc = The LC9 is a large, bulky incinerator designed for civilian use with a unique flame intensity switch on the bottom. The low-intensity setting serves as a welding torch, with the high-intensity setting used for organic matter disposal and waste clearing. The switch is jammed to the high-intensity setting.
ent-RMCTankFlamerColony = LC9 flamer tank
    .desc = A fuel tank used to store fuel for use in the LC9 incinerator unit. Handle with care.
